        <div class="lf-band">
            <p class="lf-sr">How LUPO works, and what it filters out: most inbound is noise. An anonymous visitor arrives; LUPO identifies and enriches the company behind the visit, the person on US traffic, and resolves personal-email signups by asking in the conversation. It responds in seconds across web form, email, chat, or phone and qualifies against your ICP. Vendor pitches, recruiters, and out-of-fit inbound are filtered out and never reach a rep. Real buyers are scored on fit and intent, booked into a rep's calendar, and written to your CRM with contact, score, and transcript.</p>
